d.\n\nThe SelfAuthoring Suite is good for adults who are not students as well. It provides its users with the opportunity to put old but still disturbing memories to rest, understand their personality, and plan for a productive and meaningful future. \n\n-- SUPPORT THIS CHANNEL --\n\nDirect Support: https://www.jordanbpeterson.com/donate\nMerchandise: https://teespring.com/stores/jordanbp...\n\n-- BOOKS --\n\n12 Rules for Life: An Antidote to Chaos: https://jordanbpeterson.com/12-rules-...\nMaps of Meaning: The Architecture of Belief: https://jordanbpeterson.com/maps-of-m...\n\n-- LINKS --\n\nWebsite: https://jordanbpeterson.com/\n12 Rules for Life Tour: https://jordanbpeterson.com/events/\nBlog: https://jordanbpeterson.com/blog/\nPodcast: https://jordanbpeterson.com/podcast/\nReading List: https://jordanbpeterson.com/great-books/\nTwitter:   / jordanbpeterson  \nInstagram:   / jordan.b.peterson  \nFacebook:   / drjordanpeterson  \n\n-- PRODUCTS --\n\nPersonality Course: https://www.jordanbpeterson.com/perso...\nSelf Authoring Suite: https://selfauthoring.com/\nUnderstand Myself personality test: https://understandmyself.com/\nMerchandise: https://teespring.com/stores/jordanbp...","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":592,"length":38,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBoQ040EGAciEwjJrv334pKVAxVTuDcIHbZKAhtIgqCL7u3c29epAcoBBHZE2YA=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbUR3c1FRLXp0SW4yZzJBZ05GNVFEaGhNWUsyd3xBQ3Jtc0tsQ3AwQzZtUUM2VklNaV9ITGd0R2dIbExtUGZmZkh3bWRDVUxweVBHQ1FpeXNOcVlRR1VsNHBZeTJ0MHNmUHF3bzBxcFo3VC1kaUFWUlhwaTFqZFBxd2FSSjQ3STJLd01RZ2ZTa2RmZjFhWHR3bEJDVQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jordanbpeterson.com%2Fdonate\u0026v=qa9u5t3C0AI","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbUR3c1FRLXp0SW4yZzJBZ05GNVFEaGhNWUsyd3xBQ3Jtc0tsQ3AwQzZtUUM2VklNaV9ITGd0R2d